  day1Notes: Rash\nMismatched Documents
  day2Notes: Rash AND Acne\nMismatched Documents\nNo vaccine document
  day2Half2Notes: Rash OR Acne\nMismatched Documents\nNo vaccine document\nNo Vaccine
    3
  day3Notes: Rash OR Acne OR Chest Discolouration\nAcne and chest disco = neither
    count\nMismatched Documents\nWeight Loss
  day3Half2Notes: Rash OR Acne OR Chest Discolouration\nAcne and chest disco = neither
    count\nBlood O Male = Rash doesn't count\nMismatched Documents\nWeight Loss
  day4Notes: Rash OR Acne OR Chest Discolouration\nAcne and chest disco = neither
    count\nBlood O Male = Rash doesn't count\nMismatched Documents\nWeight Loss\nIrregular
    Speech
  day4Half2Notes: Rash OR Acne OR Chest Discolouration\nAcne and chest disco = neither
    count\nBlood O Male = Rash doesn't count\nMismatched Documents\nWeight Loss\nIrregular
    Speech\nKids need diff document
  day2SubNotes: Vaccine 1 = 100% no rash\nVaccine 2 = 100% no acne
  day3SubNotes: Patterened chest disco = no acne or rash
  day4SubNotes: Yulian or Susana = Good to let through
  amountToMoveYToExpandNotes: -112
