  m_text: 'Each day you must check residents for signs of infection using the tools
    given to you


    You must update your checklist according to your findings,
    and submit once a final decision has been made


    The signs to look for today
    are as follows

    A rash on either arm

    Mismatch in Documentation (Test
    results show no infection when there are symptoms, or Test results show infection
    when there are symptoms)


    Your notes will be automatically updated to reflect
    the current signs to look out for '
